VhDir Insurance Plan Cost Qualifier

This value set defines a set of codes that further qualify the cost of a plan.

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include these codes as defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/vhdir/CodeSystem/insuranceplan
    CodeDisplay
    q1Cost QualificationThis is a sample cost qualification.
